      <item>
        <title>[Discord Poll] Final WKM Poll</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Shrimpy]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>I don’t mind WKM yet I have an idea that you might want to add to the list anyway (I did submit it on the poll):</p>
<ul>
<li>Give <strong>Illusionist</strong> and <strong>Aristocrat</strong> and  <strong>Apostle</strong> and <strong>Possessor</strong> the ability to read a player’s <em>ENTIRE</em> past whisper history.</li>
</ul>
<p>Illusionist would have the useless Mental Blur replaced with this ability.  Since Illusionist is so rare, let this new ability reveal ALL past whispers of EVERY player to the ENTIRE Unseen so that they benefit from the ability even if the Illusionist dies the night after she is converted.</p>
<p>Apostle and Aristocrat’s Court Spy would remain the same, yet become a targetable ability in order to incorporate its new power:  reading a specific player’s past whisper history (in addition to spying on the court).</p>
<p>Possessor would be able to read the entire past whisper history of anyone that he possesses or puppet-strings.  This would have the added benefit of annihilating the possword meta.</p>
          <p><a href="https://forum.throneoflies.com/t/discord-poll-final-wkm-poll/73330/19">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
